nm:output.nm:control_stream:
;; 1. Based on: 1 $PROBLEM SB vitreous
$INPUT ID TIME DV MDV CMT AMT GROUP=SKIP LEFT SITE DAY WEEK ID2=SKIP IDD=SKIP
$DATA SB.csv IGNORE=@
$SUBROUTINES ADVAN1 TRANS2
$PK CL = THETA(1)*EXP(ETA(1)) V = THETA(2)*EXP(ETA(2))
S1 = V ; dose: mg V: ng/mL
$ERROR
IPRED = F W = SQRT(THETA(3)**2 + THETA(4)**2 * IPRED**2) IRES = DV - IPRED IWRES = IRES / W Y = IPRED + W * EPS(1)
$THETA (0,0.000004) ; CL (0,0.0007) ; V 0.000001 FIX ; Additive Residual Variability (0,0.1) ; Proportional Residual Variability $OMEGA 0.1 0.1
$SIGMA 1 FIX 1 FIX
$COVARIANCE PRINT = E
$ESTIMATION NOABORT MAXEVALS=9999 METHOD=1 INTER PRINT = 10
$TABLE ID TIME DV MDV CMT AMT LEFT SITE DAY WEEK IWRES IRES IPRED CWRES NOPRINT ONEHEADER FILE=sdtab2 $TABLE ID CL V ETA1 ETA2 NOPRINT ONEHEADER NOAPPEND FILE=patab2
